{"tid":2044849,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「最美變性人」河莉秀曝悲慘童年…父曾當面酸：不該生下你","createTime":"2020-05-31T11:16:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T12:40:26.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e561c31d844a8f8af1377490581b1db91f93daa1","tid":2044849,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:16:02.000Z","msg":"現年45歲的南韓女星河莉秀因擁有天使般的俏麗臉蛋加上魔鬼般的火辣身材，被稱作是「最美變性人」。身為南韓第一位變性藝人，河莉秀不免受到外界的指指點點，即使出道多年，仍無法改變社會大眾對她的刻板印象。近日她在節目《Love on the Air》（TV는 사랑을 싣고）坦露了自己的辛酸經歷，並表示與父親的關係非常糟糕，在她決定接受變性手術的5年後，爸爸才得知此事。<br />\n<br />\n河莉秀說雖然是作為一名男性出生，但在小時候就已經覺得以一個女性的身分活著是一件理所當然的事情，喜歡大家稱讚自己漂亮，跟其他女孩們一起玩洋娃娃也覺得很自然，不過卻因為這樣和父親的關係鬧僵，非常偏愛會讀書的姐姐，甚至連別人到家裡作客，都會當面酸「當初就說不要生了，你看生下來變成那副模樣」，對年幼的河莉秀造成了極大的創傷。<br />\n<br />\n河莉秀無奈嘆「爸爸在外人的眼中是一個溫暖的人，但回到家就變得相當嚴格」，她回想起有次自己跟鄰居家的小孩吵架哭了，爸爸還因此用腳踹她，到現在她的額頭上還能看到當時留下的痕跡，「上了高中後，就再也沒和爸爸對話過了」，1995年她決定動變性手術，爸爸直到手術的5年後才知道，不過長大後的她也早已放下，「在某個瞬間，看著爸爸那個曾經讓我很害怕的背影，突然變得很渺小，我選擇原諒，決定不再恨他。」雖然家庭生活並不愉快，但她很感謝自己在高中的恩師，「因為老師的照顧，才讓我有活下去的動力」。"},{"pid":"cd79f5095218a3ece2edf5973115d6735a41b263","tid":2044849,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/31/2585136-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F31%2F2585136-XXL.jpg&h=e12f737f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲河莉秀被譽為「最美變性人」。（圖／翻攝自河莉秀IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/31/2585135-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F31%2F2585135-XXL.jpg&h=96b1a18f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6bbec7d90fa932e8341bef85e17b904ff6d04530","tid":2044849,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:16:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/31/2585137-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F31%2F2585137-XXL.jpg&h=7a8a3f10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲河莉秀變性前照片。（圖／翻攝自KBS）"},{"pid":"51a7e970df2ea9327336bdd200477495c159bee6","tid":2044849,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:16:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/31/2585138-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F31%2F2585138-XXL.jpg&h=081ea061&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲河莉秀淚訴因為性向與父親的關係非常糟糕。（圖／翻攝自KBS）"},{"pid":"d48d6339f13da6f193a9e6a77d81e0feba6e530e","tid":2044849,"uid":320204,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:17:58.000Z","msg":"彩瑛稍勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f599074595f9df47dd2e405dfa4f2a138a0a6d1","tid":2044849,"uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:18:27.000Z","msg":"本來個樣都幾靚仔 可惜"},{"pid":"bd6d78bdd8fb6fe2a624a06ac7209273fd239c12","tid":2044849,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d48d6339f13da6f193a9e6a77d81e0feba6e530e","tid":2044849,"uid":320204,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:17:58.000Z","msg":"彩瑛稍勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:19:57.000Z","msg":"彩瑛完勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65d28a0608dc2088f09d778189f5f60c5a66d91a","tid":2044849,"uid":89931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:27:43.000Z","msg":"屌打彩瑛"},{"pid":"3e9008ef3d38fbac64eedb8320fe1be41ff7c517","tid":2044849,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:29:38.000Z","msg":"version幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab22115315efee968f3b1c6ef6a92395ccc47f83","tid":2044849,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65d28a0608dc2088f09d778189f5f60c5a66d91a","tid":2044849,"uid":